  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*monodromy with no twist, diagonal twist, and companion twist*)\nClearAll[T,Tg,TG];\nT[λ1_,λ2_][i_,j_][u_]:=Sum[KroneckerProduct[L[λ1][i,ii][u-θ1],L[λ2][ii,j][u-θ2]],{ii,3}];\nTg[λ1_,λ2_][i_,j_][u_]:= z[i] T[λ1,λ2][i,j][u];\nTG[λ1_,λ2_][i_,j_][u_]:=Sum[T[λ1,λ2][i,ii][u] G[[ii,j]],{ii,3}];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*Yangian weights - eigenvalues of T[i,i] on the highest-weight state.\n  General rep: T[i,i]|hw> = (u-θ1-h λ1[[i]])(u-θ2-h λ2[[i]]) |hw>, from L[λ][i,i]|hw>=(u-h λ_i)|hw>.\n  Symmetric case λ=(S,0,0) reduces to ν[1]=(u-θ1-hS1)(u-θ2-hS2), ν[2]=ν[3]=(u-θ1)(u-θ2).*)\nClearAll[ν,HWS];\nν[λ1_,λ2_][i_][u_]:=(u-θ1-h λ1[[i]])(u-θ2-h λ2[[i]]);\nHWS[λ1_,λ2_]:=Table[{KroneckerDelta[1,ii]},{ii,1,dim[λ1] dim[λ2]}];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*checking highest-weights against the general ν, on non-symmetric reps*)\nModule[{reps={{{2,1,0},{1,0,0}},{{1,1,0},{1,1,0}},{{2,2,0},{1,0,0}},{{2,1,0},{1,1,0}}}},\n Union@Flatten@Table[\n   T[r[[1]],r[[2]]][i,i][u].HWS[r[[1]],r[[2]]]-ν[r[[1]],r[[2]]][i][u] HWS[r[[1]],r[[2]]],\n   {r,reps},{i,3}]]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"352972\" data-output-id=\"313\" data-out-n=\"37\" data-sub-idx=\"1\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"9\" data-sub-start=\"1\" data-sub-end=\"1\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[37]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mroynmag-urahsio\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcezBccmlnaHRcfQ==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[37]= \\left\\{0\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "b9eec810-0d00-48ad-9fd3-b1ff66ef90a1"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*quantum minors (q-determinants) of the monodromy matrix*)\nClearAll[qmin,qming,qminG];\nqmin[λ1_, λ2_][II_List, JJ_List][u_] := \n    qmin[λ1, λ2][II, JJ][u] = \n     Sum[Signature[σ] \n        Dot @@ Table[T[λ1, λ2][II[[σ[[k]]]], JJ[[k]]][u - (k - 1) h], {k, \n            Length[II]}], {σ, Permutations[Range[Length[II]]]}];\n\nqming[λ1_, λ2_][II_List, JJ_List][u_] := \n    qming[λ1, λ2][II, JJ][u] = \n     Sum[Signature[σ] \n        Dot @@ Table[Tg[λ1, λ2][II[[σ[[k]]]], JJ[[k]]][u - (k - 1) h], {k, \n            Length[II]}], {σ, Permutations[Range[Length[II]]]}];\n\nqminG[λ1_, λ2_][II_List, JJ_List][u_] := \n    qminG[λ1, λ2][II, JJ][u] = \n     Sum[Signature[σ] \n        Dot @@ Table[TG[λ1, λ2][II[[σ[[k]]]], JJ[[k]]][u - (k - 1) h], {k, \n            Length[II]}], {σ, Permutations[Range[Length[II]]]}];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*transfer matrices with diagonal twist*)\nClearAll[tg];\ntg[λ1_,λ2_][a_,1][u_]:= Total[qming[λ1, λ2][#, #][u] & /@ Subsets[{1, 2, 3}, {a}]]\n\n(*transfer matrices with companion twist*)\nClearAll[tG];\ntG[λ1_,λ2_][a_,1][u_]:= Total[qminG[λ1, λ2][#, #][u] & /@ Subsets[{1, 2, 3}, {a}]]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*value of quantum determinant (χ3 carried here; general ν)*)\nClearAll[qdetT];\nqdetT[λ1_,λ2_][u_]:=χ3 ν[λ1,λ2][1][u-2h] ν[λ1,λ2][2][u-h] ν[λ1,λ2][3][u];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*qdetT central value == tg[·][3,1]; on non-symmetric reps this is the ν shift-ordering guard.\n  NB: Chop wraps Simplify because z[k] (hence χ3) are high-precision *numeric* (not exact\n  symbolic) here — the verbatim Simplify[...] form leaves ~10^-27..10^-30 floating \"0``prec\"\n  coefficients multiplying u-polynomials (Times doesn't auto-collapse 0.`prec*u to 0 for\n  symbolic u), so Union@Flatten never sees a literal 0 even though every entry evaluates to\n  exactly 0. numerically (verified at random u and u=1, Max|residual|=0. exactly). Confirmed\n  this is a genuine-zero/representation artifact, not a wrong shift ordering: the reversed\n  assignment ν[3][u-2h]ν[2][u-h]ν[1][u] gives a real O(1) residual (~5.8 at u=1, reps sample),\n  clearly distinguishing \"correct but unsimplified\" from \"actually wrong\".*)\nModule[{reps={{{2,1,0},{1,0,0}},{{1,1,0},{1,1,0}},{{2,2,0},{1,0,0}},{{2,1,0},{1,1,0}}}},\n Union@Flatten@Table[\n   Chop[Simplify[qdetT[r[[1]],r[[2]]][u] idd[r[[1]],r[[2]]]-tg[r[[1]],r[[2]]][3,1][u]],10^-15],{r,reps}]]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*verify numeric parameters took hold before building Section B on top of them*)\n{Precision[χ1], N[χ3], Chip = χ1 - (z[1] + z[2] + z[3])} /. Chip -> Chop[Chip]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"352972\" data-output-id=\"315\" data-out-n=\"49\" data-sub-idx=\"1\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"14\" data-sub-start=\"1\" data-sub-end=\"1\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[49]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mroyo05a-tw0i8im\" data-page-width-em=\"21\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcezI5Ljk5ODQxNTYyNDk5OTczMywtMC45OTQ0MTQ1OTc4NDE1Mjg2LTAuMTA1NTQ0MzM5NDk2MTEzMzNcLFxtYXRocm17aX0sMFxyaWdodFx9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">29.998415624999733</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">0.9944145978415286</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.10554433949611333</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
