  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* NB: exploratory, not used by alphaCoeffs — ee[λ1,λ2][i,i] was never defined even in V1 (stayed\n   symbolic), so this cell has always been a scratch expression, not a validated formula. *)\ntasympt[1,1]=u^2 χ1 - \n         u (θ1 + θ2) χ1 - \n         h u Sum[z[ii] ee[λ1, λ2][ii, ii],{ii,3}]",
